1616
01:22:52,968 --> 01:22:57,110
So, who wants to
test my powers first?

1617
01:22:59,975 --> 01:23:01,454
You?

1618
01:23:06,247 --> 01:23:08,124
You?

1619
01:23:09,451 --> 01:23:10,657
